    {
        "content": "<p>Resurrecting this to seek feedback, here's a draft PR: <a href=\"https://github.com/Rust-for-Linux/linux/pull/1036\">https://github.com/Rust-for-Linux/linux/pull/1036</a> -- <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"411647\">@Boqun Feng</span> I added you as a codeveloper.</p>\n<p>I'm using <code>WithRef</code> as the name, it was suggested by <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"412316\">@bjorn3</span> at some point. I added a tag saying that it was his suggestion.</p>\n<p>I intend to send this small series to the mailing list soonish.</p>",
