    {
        "content": "<p>FWIW: I cherry-picked Wedon's two commit onto the latest <code>rust-dev</code>: <a href=\"https://github.com/fbq/linux/commits/rust-dev-with-ref\">https://github.com/fbq/linux/commits/rust-dev-with-ref</a>, fixed a few conflicts and also reorder a few changes from patch 2 to patch 1 to make it compile for each individual patch.</p>",
