    {
        "content": "<p>Thanks for taking a look, folks!</p>\n<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"411647\">@Boqun Feng</span> I think we can deal with the conflicts as they arise. I think (hope?) they'll be simple enough. Also thanks for the heads up that the first commit wasn't build on its own, I fixed that.</p>\n<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"498029\">@Andreas Hindborg</span> The <code>ArcInner</code> name is gone; what we're making public is <code>WithRef&lt;T&gt;</code> -- the intent of the name is to indicate that it's a T with a ref-count attached to it.</p>",
        "id": 392225024,
        "sender_full_name": "Wedson Almeida Filho",
        "timestamp": 1695255799
    },
