    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"531558\">@Wedson Almeida Filho</span>  before the pr, we still use the GAT.  So which one feature of GAT  lead you to just use the &amp;Arcinner&lt;T&gt;, and remove the ArcBorrow. I dont get it, can you explain this?</p>",
